<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">عَنْ عَائِشَةَ <span class="special">﵂</span>:</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>لَمَّا نَزَلَتْ آيَاتُ سُورَةِ الْبَقَرَةِ عَنْ آخِرِهَا، خَرَجَ النَّبِيُّ صَلَّى اللَّهُ عَلَيْهِ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">وَسَلَّمَ فَقَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">(حُرِّمَتِ التِّجَارَةُ فِي الْخَمْرِ)</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
